@page "/"

<PageTitle>WildFireSim</PageTitle>

<div class="jumbotron text-center mt-4">
    <h1 class="display-4">WildFireSim</h1>
    <p class="lead">An interactive wildfire simulation built with Blazor.</p>
    <a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" href="wildfire">Run the Simulation</a>
</div>

<div class="container mb-5">
    <h2>About the project</h2>
    <p>
        WildFireSim demonstrates how fires spread across different terrains while
        considering wind direction and embers. The simulator lets you tweak
        probabilities and visualize the results directly in your browser.
    </p>
    <p>
        This project showcases the power of .NET and Blazor for real-time
        interactive applications.
    </p>
</div>
